[normal]Q1 [bold]&#xa0; 
[normal]Chair[bold]:[bold] Good morning, Minister
[normal],
[normal] and thank you for being available to speak to us today on the departmental Annual Report.
[normal] 
[normal]We are short of time, so I will just quickly ask everyone to introduce themselves for voice transcription purposes and then we will get on.
[normal]Martin [bold]Donnelly:[bold] [bold]I am Martin 
[normal]Donnelly, Permanent Secretary of the Department.
[normal]Vince [bold]Cable:[bold] Vinc
[normal]e 
[normal]Cable, Secretary of State.
